    BaseRequestListener<org.json.JSONObject>

    public abstract class JSONRequestListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements BaseRequestListener<org.json.JSONObject>
    Server request listener Every listener is supposed to implement own BaseRequestListener.onError(com.doodeec.utils.network.RequestError) method Every listener should also implement (override) one of onSuccess methods onSuccess(org.json.JSONObject) or onSuccess(org.json.JSONArray)
